Developer Terms of Use
des: The Waukesha County Custard assistant will let you know of the Flavors of the Day at various custard shops all over Waukesha County, including Brookfield, Waukesha, and other local towns. You can also get info about each of the stores, including locations and hours. Need help? Just ask "Waukesha County Custard, what can you tell me?"
